                                                                    <p>We need to somehow tell Twig about our fun new Twig extension. To do that, first,
register it as a service. The name doesn't matter, so how about <code>app.markdown_extension</code>.
Set the class, but skip <code>arguments</code>: we don't have any yet, so this is optional:</p>
